pty Nest (TV series)|Empty Nest]]\" - \"Life Goes On\" by [[Billy Vera]]\n*\"[[Free Spirit (TV series)|Free Spirit]]\"\n*\"[[Growing Pains]]\" - \"As Long as We Got Each Other\" by [[B.J. Thomas]], [[Jennifer Warnes]], [[Dusty Springfield]], [[Kim Carnes]], \"Swept Away\" by [[Christopher Cross]]\n*\"[[Guiding Light]]\" - \"Where There is Hope\"\n*\"[[Just the Ten of Us]]\" - \"Doin' it the Best I Can\" by [[Bill Medley]], \"Lock Up Your Daughters\" by [[Don Barnes]]\n*\"[[Major Dad]]\"\n*\"[[Murphy Brown]] - \"Like the Whole World's Watching\" by [[Take 6]]\n*\"[[Nurses (TV series)|Nurses]]\" - \"Here I Am\"\n*[[Summer olympics 1988|Summer Olympics '88]]- \"[[One Moment in Time]]\" by [[Whitney Houston]]\n*\"[[Uncle Buck (1990 TV series)|Uncle Buck]]\" - \"Uncle Buck\" by [[Ronnie Milsap]]\n\n==Uses in Television and Film==\n\n===Film===\n*''[[13 Going on 30]]'' - \"[[Crazy for You (Madonna song)|Crazy for You]]\" by [[Madonna (entertainer)|Madonna]]\n*''[[American Heart (film)|American Heart]]'' - \"[[Slow Hand]]\" by [[Pointer Sisters]]\n*''[[Double Dare (film)|Double Dare]]'' - \"[[Top of the World (The Carpenters song)|Top of the World]]\" by [[The Carpenters]]\n*''[[Free Willy]]'' - \"Right Here (Human Nature Remix)\" by [[SWV]]\n*''[[High School High]]'' - \"[[Top of the World (The Carpenters song)|Top of the World]]\" by [[The Carpenters]]\n*''[[Johnny Be Good]]'' - \"Perfect Stranger\"\n*''[[The Last Supper]]'' - \"[[Top of the World (The Carpenters song)|Top of the World]]\" by [[The Carpenters]]\n*''[[The Parent Trap (1998 film)|The Parent Trap]]'' - \"[[Top of the World (The Carpenters song)|Top of the World]]\" by [[The Carpenters]]\n*''Road to Alice'' - \"[[Top of the World (The Carpenters song)|Top of the World]]\" by [[The Carpenters]]\n*''[[S.F.W.]]'' - \"As Long As We Got Each Other\" performed by [[Stephen Dorff]]\n*''[[Showdown in Little Tokyo]]'' - \"[[Top of the World (The Carpenters song)|Top of the World]]\" by [[The Carpenters|Carpenters]]\n