 Cross]]\n*\"[[Nights Are Forever (Jennifer Warnes song)|Nights Are Forever]]\" by [[Jennifer Warnes]]\n\n== O ==\n*\"Once I Get Over You by [[Ronnie Milsap]]\n*\"Once in a While by Billy Dean\n*\"One Love by [[The Carpenters]]\n*\"One Moment by [[Steve Quinzi]]\n*\"[[One Moment in Time]]\" by [[Whitney Houston]]\n*\"[[One of a Kind Pair of Fools]]\" by [[Barbara Mandrell]]\n*\"[[Only One Love in My Life (song)|Only One Love in My Life\"]] by [[Ronnie Milsap]]\n*\"[[Only Yesterday (song)|Only Yesterday]]\" by [[The Carpenters]]\n*\"Only You Will Do\" by [[2nd Nature (band)|2nd Nature]]\n*\"[[Legend (1985 film)#Songs in the film|Oona / The Jewels]]\" by [[Jerry Goldsmith]]\n*\"Over My Head Again\" by [[Jackie Deshannon]]\n\n== P ==\n*\"Pa Varidens Tak\" by [[Vikingarna (band)|Vikingarna]]\n*\"Perfectly Alone\" by [[Carol Burnett]]\n*\"[[Promise Me You'll Remember (Love Theme from The Godfather Part III)|Promise Me You\u2019ll Remember]]\" by [[Harry Connick Jr.]]\n\n== R ==\n*\"Reachin for a little bit More by [[Marshall Tucker Band]]\n*\"Remember When\" by [[Ray Vega (singer)|Ray Vega]]\n*\"Requiem for a Lightweight by [[Mark Morales (rapper)|Mark Morales]]\n*\"Rhapsody for Now: Live and Let Die\" by [[Doc Severinsen]]\n*\"Rhythm in My Heart\" by [[Stacy Earl]]\n*\"[[Right Here/Human Nature]]\" by [[SWV]]\n*\"Running Alone\" by [[Steve Perry]]\n\n== S ==\n*\"Sailing the Tide\" by [[The Carpenters]]\n*\"Same Old Feeling\" by [[38 Special (band)|.38 Special]]\n*\"Sandy\" by [[The Carpenters]]\n*\"Saturday\" by [[The Carpenters]]\n*\"[[She Ain't You|She Ain\u2019t You]]\" by [[Chris Brown (American entertainer)|Chris Brown]]\n*\"Say it Simple\" by [[Sixwire]]\n*\"Since You Walked into My Life\" by [[New Kids on the Block]]\n*\"Sing for the Children\" by [[Ben Tankard]]\n*\"Sing the Wee\" by [[Jerry Goldsmith]]\n*\"Skyline\" by [[Brian Mitchell (musician)|Brian Mitchell]]\n*\"[[Slow Hand]] by [[Conway Twitty]], [[Pointer Sisters]]\n*\"So Hard Living Without You\" by Air